    "m_Title": "Toggle Workflows",
    "m_Content": "CheckMetallic is a custom function node checking whether keyword _SPECULAR_SETUP is enabled. If it is enabled, the workflow is set to specular, the specular group of nodes will be used. Vise versa, if _SPECULAR_SETUP is disabled the metallic group of nodes will be used.",
